        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Catullioides rubrolineata Bierman A male, dorsal view B female, dorsal view C male, lateral view D female, lateral view. Scale bars: 2 mm." , "Figure 8. Catullioides taishunensis sp. nov. A male pygofer, gonostyles, and segment X, left lateral view B male pygofer, gonostyles, and segment X, right lateral view C male segment X and pygofer, dorsal view D male pygofer and gonostyles, ventral view E aedeagus, dorsal view F aedeagus, left lateral view G aedeagus, right lateral view H aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." , "Figure 7. Catullioides taishunensis sp. nov. A head, pronotum and mesonotum, dorsal view B head and pronotum, lateral view C head and pronotum, ventral view D forewing E hindwing. Scale bars: 1 mm." , "Figure 6. Catullioides taishunensis sp. nov. A male, photographed by Z-S Song B male, dorsal view C male, lateral view. Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/543789" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/543795" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/543794" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/543793" .

